# License / 利用規約

## 1. Secondary Creation Policy / 二次創作に関するガイドライン

This project, "Figura Blue Archive Crafters," is a fan-made secondary creation based on "Blue Archive" owned by NEXON Games Co., Ltd. & Yostar, Inc.

本作品（Figura Blue Archive Crafters）は、NEXON Games Co., Ltd. および Yostar, Inc. が権利を所有する「ブルーアーカイブ」の二次創作コンテンツです。

- Official Guidelines: Users must comply with the official "Blue Archive" Secondary Creation Guidelines.
- Ownership of IP: All rights to character designs, EX skill animations, and related visual assets belong to NEXON Games / Yostar. Any use that violates the official guidelines is strictly prohibited.
- Official Guidelines (JP): <https://bluearchive.jp/fankit/guidelines>

## 2. Ownership & Scope / 権利の所在と適用範囲

We distinguish between official intellectual property and the original work created for this project as follows:

本プロジェクトでは、公式の知的財産と独自制作部分を以下の通り区別しています。

### Gakuto1112 (Author) Rights

- Original 3D model data (meshes/textures) created by Gakuto1112.
- Original programs, including Lua scripts and build scripts (Excluding the logo displayed in the build tool).
- The MIT License applies to these "Programs" and "Original Data Structures."

### Official Rights

- The visual design, motifs, and branding of the characters.
- Commercial use or sale of this project (as a whole) is strictly prohibited in accordance with the official guidelines.

## 3. Prohibited Acts / 禁止事項

To protect the creative community, the following acts are strictly prohibited:

創作コミュニティを保護するため、以下の行為を固く禁止します。

- Plagiarism & Impersonation (自作発言の禁止):
  Do not claim this work (or modified versions of it) as your own original creation. Please credit the original author (Gakuto1112) when sharing or distributing.
- Violation of Official Rules:
  Any use that damages the reputation of the original copyright holders.

